{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So that was in, in-- he was deported on the 9th of May, 1942, address unknown.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we didn't know where the people went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for one year, I, I just-- I just was going nuts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just wanted to know what did I do?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What happened?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What happened to him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So eventually, I had this terribly crazy idea that what if I go to the Jewish Council and ask them, because I'm half Jewish, why can't I be in the transport?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because a lot of half Jewish people were there, only that they had Jewish religion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't have, so big deal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What's the difference?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that if-- if they could put me in the transport?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they thought I'm a naughty teenager, you know, and they hardly even talked to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But there was one very nice man, a young man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he sort of understood a little bit my torment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, look, they only thing you can do is if you convert to Judaism, then we can transport you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so he thought, oh well, I got rid of her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I got the address of a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to go really for real, to write a bit in Hebrew, and to say a prayer, and to learn the customs of, of Jewish women, what to do and what not to do, which all didn't interest me at all.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when the rabbi finally was satisfied, I went and had the mikveh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And after I was in the mikveh, I went to the authorities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had to go to the Czech authorities to say that I am no longer Evangelic, that I am now a Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put it in some big book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I went to Jewish Council.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
